            </div>
            <div class="pivot-card" style="background: var(--dark-surface); padding: 20px; border-radius: 12px; text-align: center;">
                <div style="font-size: 1.25rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--theme-color);">Netflix</div>
                <div style="color: var(--text-muted); margin: 8px 0;">DVD mailing</div>
                <div style="font-size: 1.5rem;">‚Üì</div>
                <div style="color: var(--text-secondary);">Streaming</div>
            </div>
            <div class="pivot-card" style="background: var(--dark-surface); padding: 20px; border-radius: 12px; text-align: center;">
                <div style="font-size: 1.25rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--theme-color);">Twitter</div>
                <div style="color: var(--text-muted); margin: 8px 0;">Podcasting</div>
                <div style="font-size: 1.5rem;">‚Üì</div>
                <div style="color: var(--text-secondary);">Microblogging</div>
            </div>
            <div class="pivot-card" style="background: var(--dark-surface); padding: 20px; border-radius: 12px; text-align: center;">
                <div style="font-size: 1.25rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--theme-color);">Shopify</div>
                <div style="color: var(--text-muted); margin: 8px 0;">Snowboard store</div>
                <div style="font-size: 1.5rem;">‚Üì</div>
                <div style="color: var(--text-secondary);">E-commerce platform</div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </StandardSlide>

    <!-- Slide 14: Customer First -->
    <StatementSlide id="14" title="Customer First">
        Everything starts with the customer.
        <span class="subtext" style="display: block; font-size: 1.5rem; color: var(--text-secondary); margin-top: 20px; font-weight: 400;">Not your idea. Not your technology. The customer.</span>
    </StatementSlide>

    <!-- Slide 15: Pirate + SEAL -->
    <StandardSlide id="15" title="The Entrepreneurial Mindset" type="visual">
        <div class="dual-cards">
            <div class="dual-card">
                <div class="icon">üè¥‚Äç‚ò†Ô∏è</div>
                <h3>Spirit of a Pirate</h3>
                <p>Challenge the status quo. Question assumptions. Be bold.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="dual-card">
                <div class="icon">üéØ</div>
                <h3>Skills of a Navy SEAL</h3>
                <p>Disciplined execution. Systematic approach. Data-driven decisions.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </StandardSlide>

    <!-- Slide 16: Course Overview Section -->
    <StatementSlide id="16" section="The Course" title="What We'll Build">
        <span class="section-label" style="display: block; font-size: 1.2rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 2px; color: var(--text-muted); margin-bottom: 15px;">This Semester</span>
        What We'll Build Together
    </StatementSlide>

    <!-- Slide 17: Course Timeline -->
    <StandardSlide id="17" title="Your 10-Week Journey" type="visual">
        <div class="timeline">
            <div class="timeline-item">
                <div class="timeline-dot">1-2</div>
